        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend section 412(a)(2) of the Immigration and Nationality Act to require ratification of a plan with respect to a refugee by the legislature of a State before the refugee may be initially placed or resettled in the State, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
